This paper discusses the scheduling of jobs in distributed machine learning systems, which involves topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
